data.description: Listen up future homeowner, I've got the property of your dreams - or should I say schemes! This triple decker will give you the most bang for your buck. You'll have not one, not two, but three rooms to stash all your stuff. That's right, three bedrooms for all your worldly possessions and then some. You can make one an office, one a craft room, heck even turn one into a ball pit if that's your thing. And when nature calls, you've got not one but two bathrooms to answer. No more fighting over the porcelain throne! You'll be living like royalty with that much bathroom real estate. But I'm not done yet. This baby comes with a double car garage to park your rides and still have space left over for your tools and workshop. Plus a covered patio where you can host parties, avoid the sun, and cook up a storm. What are you waiting for? This deal is too good to be true, but I'm offering it to you anyway. The keys are just waiting to be yours!
